372
00:22:40,390 --> 00:22:41,580
來吧
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MAN: Here we go now.{\r}

373
00:22:52,860 --> 00:22:54,900
-對不起 -骰子
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Oh, I'm sorry. -The dice.{\r}

374
00:22:56,900 --> 00:22:58,700
多謝
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you very much.{\r}

375
00:23:00,580 --> 00:23:02,030
多謝你
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I appreciate that.{\r}

376
00:23:02,740 --> 00:23:05,280
保重，史蒂夫 要冒險啊，開快車
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Take care, Steve. Take chances, drive fast.{\r}

377
00:23:06,460 --> 00:23:08,910
這一百給你，甜心 多謝你賞光
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This $100 is for you, love. Thanks for your time.{\r}

378
00:23:10,550 --> 00:23:12,370
-快點 -怎么了？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Come on. -What's the matter?{\r}

379
00:23:13,380 --> 00:23:16,090
我幫你賺了不少，我要我的份
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I made a lot of money for you, I want my cut.{\r}

380
00:23:16,220 --> 00:23:18,010
什么錢？我看到你偷錢
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What money? I've seen you stealing.{\r}

381
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:20,510
“什么錢？” 你看看這堆籌碼
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}"What money?" Look at the stack of chips.{\r}

382
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,850
-我要我的一半 -我觀察你一夜了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I want my half. GAMBLER: I've watched you.{\r}

383
00:23:22,930 --> 00:23:25,310
-我要我的錢 -你皮包里全是熟籌碼
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I want my money. -Your bag is full of chips.{\r}

384
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:27,890
-我才沒偷你的東西 -滾吧！
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: I didn't steal anything from you. GAMBLER: Get lost!{\r}

385
00:23:28,820 --> 00:23:30,270
-滾吧？ -沒錯！
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Get lost? GAMBLER: Yes!{\r}

386
00:23:30,740 --> 00:23:33,060
-這怎么樣呢？ -別這樣！
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Well, how about that? -Come on!{\r}

387
00:24:24,210 --> 00:24:27,330
真酷，讓我一見鐘情
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: What a move. I fell in love right there.{\r}

388
00:24:27,470 --> 00:24:31,000
但在賭城，像金吉兒這樣的女孩 得花上大錢
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But in Vegas, for a girl like Ginger, love costs money.{\r}

389
00:24:36,810 --> 00:24:38,520
我去補個妝
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna go powder my nose.{\r}

390
00:24:49,740 --> 00:24:52,910
-金吉兒的人生目標是錢 -馬上回來
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Ginger's mission in life was money. I'll be right back.{\r}

391
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:55,080
-待會見，金吉兒 -多謝你
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}DOORMAN: See you. GINGER: Thanks for asking.{\r}

392
00:24:55,170 --> 00:24:56,870
她在賭場可是皇后
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: She was a queen around the casino.{\r}

393
00:24:57,000 --> 00:25:00,420
她召來大賭客 并也幫他們花大錢
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}She brought in high rollers and helped them spend a lot of money.{\r}

394
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:03,000
-你好 -嘿，金吉兒，你好嗎？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Hello. -Hey, Ginger. How you doing?{\r}

395
00:25:03,090 --> 00:25:05,800
好得很，一點小意思 你幫我搞定了嗎？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Great. You might have something for me. Got me covered?{\r}

396
00:25:06,850 --> 00:25:09,140
-非常感謝 -自己保重喔
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: Thank you. VALET: Take care of yourself.{\r}

397
00:25:09,220 --> 00:25:11,300
我有些幸運丸給你，安迪
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I got some lucky pills for you, Andy.{\r}

398
00:25:11,940 --> 00:25:14,640
誰不想要金吉兒？ 她是城里名聲最響亮…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Who didn't want her? She was one of the best known...{\r}

399
00:25:14,770 --> 00:25:17,860
也是道上最受歡迎的江湖人物
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}best liked and most respected hustlers in town.{\r}

400
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:24,150
像她這么聰明的玩家 可以讓男人…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Smart hustlers like her could keep a guy awake...{\r}

401
00:25:24,240 --> 00:25:26,700
兩三天不睡 然后再讓他一文不名的…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}for two or three days before sending him home broke...{\r}

402
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:28,910
回到老婆與銀行審查主任身邊
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}to the little woman and his bank examiners.{\r}

403
00:25:44,220 --> 00:25:45,600
有找錢嗎？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Any change?{\r}

404
00:25:46,770 --> 00:25:50,270
我回來時小賭了幾把
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I hit a few games on the way back.{\r}

405
00:25:51,610 --> 00:25:54,690
那根本是胡扯 她把錢收起來了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: But that was all bullshit. She just pocketed the cash.{\r}

406
00:25:57,570 --> 00:25:59,450
-你今天好嗎？ -不錯啊
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: How you doing tonight? CASHlER: Good.{\r}

407
00:25:59,570 --> 00:26:01,120
-你呢？ -衰死了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}CASHlER: How are you? GINGER: Beat.{\r}

408
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:04,110
-金吉兒洞悉玩家們的習性 -給你一百
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Ginger had the hustlers' code. GINGER: Take one for you.{\r}

409
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:07,830
-多謝 -她懂得如何買通他人
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}CASHlER: Thank you. SAM: She knew how to take care of people.{\r}

410
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:10,030
這就是賭城的座右銘
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's what Vegas is all about.{\r}

411
00:26:10,170 --> 00:26:12,620
-六千八百元 -謝啦
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}CASHlER: $6,800. GINGER: Thanks.{\r}

412
00:26:12,760 --> 00:26:15,290
-這里是講究回扣的城市 -晚安
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: It's kickback city. GINGER: Have a good night.{\r}

413
00:26:21,180 --> 00:26:23,090
她罩莊家…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: She took care of the dealers...{\r}

414
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:25,510
賭區經理，管場經理…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}pit bosses, floor managers...{\r}

415
00:26:25,900 --> 00:26:28,350
但尤其關照停車小弟…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}but, mostly, the valet parkers...{\r}

416
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:31,730
他們能幫你找到任何東西 也能幫你解決任何事
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the guys who could get you anything and take care of anything.{\r}

417
00:26:31,860 --> 00:26:33,570
金吉兒搞定了停車的…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Ginger took care of the parkers...{\r}

418
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:37,150
他們搞定警衛 而警衛會擺平警察…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}who took care of the security guards, who took care of the cops...{\r}

419
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:39,660
-讓她可繼續開工 -我今晚需要那東西
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}who let her operate. I need that stuff tonight.{\r}

420
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:42,240
-沒問題 -你真好
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}VALET: No problem. GINGER: You are a doll.{\r}

421
00:26:42,620 --> 00:26:44,870
停車賺的錢多到…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: The valet parking job was such a money-maker...{\r}

422
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:48,160
得買通酒店經理才能排上空缺
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}they had to pay off the hotel manager just to get the concession.{\r}

423
00:26:50,170 --> 00:26:52,380
不過有一點我不懂…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But one thing I didn't understand...{\r}

424
00:26:52,510 --> 00:26:54,970
她將一切都控制的好好的…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}was that she had everything under control...{\r}

425
00:26:55,140 --> 00:26:57,840
卻被她那拉皮條的男友 萊絲特戴蒙德吃得死死的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}except for her old pimp boyfriend, Lester Diamond.{\r}

426
00:26:57,980 --> 00:27:00,220
我得顧到其他人，我的搭擋們
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I got other people in this. I got partners.{\r}

427
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:05,220
在這事上有我罩你，知道嗎？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm looking out for you in this thing, okay?{\r}

428
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:09,180
你將獲你應得的 而且第一個拿到，好嗎？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You'll get yours back, and you'll get it back first. Okay?{\r}

429
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:11,530
-好的 -你去哪兒了？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-All right. -Where you going?{\r}

430
00:27:12,830 --> 00:27:14,570
你在哪兒？ 你又飄走了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Where are you? You're in that place.{\r}

431
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:16,570
-我在這兒 -不，你不在
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I'm here. -No, you're not.{\r}

432
00:27:16,710 --> 00:27:17,740
你在哪？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Where are you?{\r}

433
00:27:19,830 --> 00:27:21,380
我永遠在你身邊
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm always here for you.{\r}

434
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,960
-真的 -是啊
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You are. -I am.{\r}

435
00:27:26,010 --> 00:27:28,550
我所認識的金吉兒 根本不會多看這怪胎一眼
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: The Ginger I knew wouldn't even look at this creep.{\r}

436
00:27:30,010 --> 00:27:31,670
-祝你好運 -是啊
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Good luck. -Yeah.{\r}

437
00:27:32,010 --> 00:27:33,720
他是個老千，專作假牌…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: He was a moocher, a card cheat...{\r}

438
00:27:33,850 --> 00:27:36,520
老在高爾夫俱樂部招搖撞騙 一個癟三…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}a country club golf hustler, a scumbag...{\r}

439
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:39,520
-為了幾塊錢追著牙醫屁股跑 -小心點
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-chasing dentists for a few bucks. -Careful.{\r}

440
00:27:39,690 --> 00:27:42,020
他永遠都沒錢，永遠都有藉口
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: He was always broke. He always had a story.{\r}

441
00:27:42,150 --> 00:27:44,190
不知為何，她卻拒絕不了他
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Somehow, she could never turn him down.{\r}

442
00:27:44,530 --> 00:27:47,820
在金吉兒眼里，他只是運氣不好
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The way Ginger saw it was that he was just an unlucky guy.{\r}

443
00:27:48,030 --> 00:27:49,860
總得有人照顧他
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Somebody had to take care of him.{\r}

444
00:27:50,490 --> 00:27:51,530
在老家
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}BACK HOME{\r}

445
00:27:51,620 --> 00:27:53,410
但尼奇可不需要人照顧
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But nobody had to take care of Nicky.{\r}

446
00:27:53,540 --> 00:27:56,210
你找到現金的話 我們就跟你平分
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You find any cash in there, we'll whack it up with you.{\r}

447
00:27:56,290 --> 00:27:58,500
他把自己照顧得太好了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: He took care of himself only too well.{\r}

448
00:27:58,840 --> 00:28:01,380
這也是為什么老家的條子 都想抓他到案
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's why every badge back home wanted to nail him.{\r}

449
00:28:01,510 --> 00:28:05,130
我將這些都折得好好的 能不能放尊重點
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I folded these things beautifully. I would appreciate a little respect.{\r}

450
00:28:05,390 --> 00:28:07,590
別看我，兄弟 我還得跟她同床共枕
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Don't look at me, pal, I gotta live with her.{\r}

451
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:11,430
就連去渡個假 他們在機場時都不放過他
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Even after a vacation, they hassled him at the airport.{\r}

452
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:14,270
法蘭克瑪雷諾在那兒等他 條子們也在
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Frank Marino was there to meet him. So were the cops.{\r}

453
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:16,110
他們想逮他…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They wanted to pinch him...{\r}

454
00:28:16,190 --> 00:28:18,730
-因為一宗在安特衛普的鉆石竊案 -幫忙折吧
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-for a diamond burglary in Antwerp. -Help me fold these.{\r}

455
00:28:18,820 --> 00:28:21,850
他們隨時愿意嫁禍于他 不管是在哪兒發生什么事
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: They were ready to blame him for anything, no matter where.{\r}

456
00:28:22,320 --> 00:28:23,700
他們通常是對的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They were usually right.{\r}

457
00:28:24,740 --> 00:28:26,570
因為尼奇很喜歡混幫派
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Because Nicky enjoyed being a gangster.{\r}

458
00:28:26,700 --> 00:28:29,030
他也不在乎有誰知道
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And he didn't give a damn who knew it.{\r}

459
00:28:29,120 --> 00:28:31,580
看看，美極了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}GINGER: There we go. Look at that. Beautiful!{\r}

460
00:28:32,750 --> 00:28:34,130
讓我擔心的是…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: I mean that's what worried me...{\r}

461
00:28:34,250 --> 00:28:37,290
尼奇似乎要被派來拉斯維加斯
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}'cause it turns out, Nicky was about to be sent to Vegas.{\r}

462
00:28:37,420 --> 00:28:39,460
-好了，就這樣 -還有
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}JENNlFER: All right, we're clear. NICKY: There's more.{\r}

463
00:28:41,260 --> 00:28:43,140
一定還有些卡在里面
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: There's a couple stuck in there.{\r}

464
00:28:43,260 --> 00:28:45,090
-我告訴你都拿出來了 -快
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I'm telling you, they're out! -Come on.{\r}

465
00:28:45,220 --> 00:28:48,340
別急于辯護 可能還有些卡在你頭發里
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Don't get so defensive, it could be stuck in your hair.{\r}

466
00:28:50,270 --> 00:28:51,730
那是什么？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What's that?{\r}

467
00:28:52,610 --> 00:28:54,600
沒有了，謝謝
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}There's no more. Thanks.{\r}

468
00:28:54,780 --> 00:28:57,610
我迫不及待想去拉斯維加斯
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: I couldn't wait to get my hands on Vegas.{\r}

469
00:28:57,820 --> 00:29:00,490
但老大可不是送我去玩的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But the bosses didn't send me out to have a good time.{\r}

470
00:29:00,620 --> 00:29:03,620
他們要我去確保 沒人找艾斯的麻煩
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They sent me out to make sure that nobody fucked with Ace.{\r}

471
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:06,240
也確保沒人干擾每月的抽頭
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And nobody interfered with the fucking skim.{\r}

472
00:29:08,670 --> 00:29:10,040
-嘿 -你好嗎？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Hey. -Hey, how you doing?{\r}

473
00:29:11,130 --> 00:29:12,500
嘿，山姆
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Sammy.{\r}

474
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:16,500
-天呀，瞧瞧這地方 -不可思議
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Boy, look at this place. -Incredible.{\r}

475
00:29:17,300 --> 00:29:18,760
歡迎來賭城
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Welcome to Vegas.{\r}

476
00:29:18,850 --> 00:29:20,420
-好樣的，山姆 -不錯吧
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Okay, Sammy. SAM: Something, huh?{\r}

