490
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:02,560
當然羅 但我得告訴你…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Sure, you do. But I just gotta tell you...{\r}

491
00:30:02,690 --> 00:30:04,600
在這兒可不能開玩笑
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}it's no joke out here.{\r}

492
00:30:04,730 --> 00:30:06,770
你得保持低調
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You gotta keep a low profile.{\r}

493
00:30:06,900 --> 00:30:09,770
不像是在老家 這兒他們不喜歡我們
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It's not like back home. They don't like guys like us.{\r}

494
00:30:09,910 --> 00:30:11,860
警長是個不折不扣的牛仔
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}This sheriff's a real cowboy.{\r}

495
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:14,650
連巡警都不怕在沙漠里埋人
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Even coppers aren't afraid to bury people in the desert.{\r}

496
00:30:14,740 --> 00:30:17,620
我不在乎 我只想離開老家一陣子
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I don't care. I want to get away from back home for a while.{\r}

497
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:19,790
我厭倦了那里
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm tired of that shit back there.{\r}

498
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:21,660
看看這地方，簡直是錢砌的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Look at this place. It's made of money.{\r}

499
00:30:21,840 --> 00:30:23,210
知道最屌的是什么？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}You know what the best part is?{\r}

500
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:25,290
沒人知道我們在干嘛
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody's gonna know what we're doing.{\r}

501
00:30:25,380 --> 00:30:28,420
沒人看著我們，大家都在老家
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}There's nobody here to see us. Everybody's back home.{\r}

502
00:30:28,550 --> 00:30:30,340
我無緣故被逮了兩次
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I got pinched twice for no reason.{\r}

503
00:30:30,470 --> 00:30:32,050
我真得小心了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I really gotta be careful.{\r}

504
00:30:32,270 --> 00:30:34,800
我管理的地方是有執照的 全是合法的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm running a licensed place. Everything's legit.{\r}

505
00:30:34,890 --> 00:30:37,470
別擔心，我什么都不會做的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry about it. I'm not gonna do anything.{\r}

506
00:30:37,600 --> 00:30:40,060
我尤其不會拖你下水
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm especially not gonna involve you in anything.{\r}

507
00:30:43,780 --> 00:30:45,400
艾斯看賭城的觀點…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Ace saw Vegas one way...{\r}

508
00:30:45,570 --> 00:30:47,780
-你跟他說過我要來嗎？ -當然
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Call and tell him I'm coming? JACK: Of course.{\r}

509
00:30:47,910 --> 00:30:49,490
我的看法不同
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}...but I saw it another.{\r}

510
00:30:49,580 --> 00:30:52,030
我視它為未開發的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I saw it as untouched.{\r}

511
00:30:54,250 --> 00:30:58,080
多的是可勒索的賭馬組頭 皮條客與毒販…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They had bookies, pimps, and drug dealers I could shake down.{\r}

512
00:30:58,250 --> 00:31:00,130
他們能找誰靠？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Who the fuck were they gonna run to?{\r}

513
00:31:00,260 --> 00:31:02,080
我開始一個一個下手
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}So I started getting everybody in line.{\r}

514
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:04,890
最屌的是，我這輩子第一次…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Best of all, for the first time in my life...{\r}

515
00:31:04,970 --> 00:31:07,340
發覺了穩贏的方法
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I figured out a way not to lose.{\r}

516
00:31:07,470 --> 00:31:09,300
他是有個穩贏之計
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: He had a foolproof scheme.{\r}

517
00:31:09,430 --> 00:31:11,470
雖然不高明，但起碼行得通
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}It wasn't very scientific, but it worked.{\r}

518
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,890
他贏時就收錢
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}When he won, he collected.{\r}

519
00:31:13,060 --> 00:31:15,550
輸時就叫賭馬組頭去死
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}When he lost, he told the bookies to fuck off.{\r}

520
00:31:15,650 --> 00:31:19,230
他們能怎樣？逼迫尼奇？ 尼奇就是逼迫者
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}What were they gonna do? Muscle Nicky? Nicky was the muscle.{\r}

521
00:31:19,950 --> 00:31:21,740
-你好嗎？ -你好嗎？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Hey, how you doing? -How you doing?{\r}

522
00:31:22,780 --> 00:31:24,820
-你有東西給我嗎？ -什么東西？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You got that thing for me? -What thing?{\r}

523
00:31:24,950 --> 00:31:26,690
尼奇，我以為你是來下注的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Nicky, I thought you was laying.{\r}

524
00:31:27,120 --> 00:31:28,990
下注？不，我來收錢
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I was laying? No, I'm taking it.{\r}

525
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,950
-你確定？ -非常
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You sure? -I'm positive.{\r}

526
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:35,420
-我搞混了 -你搞混了？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-I'm a little confused. -You're a little confused?{\r}

527
00:31:36,170 --> 00:31:38,880
或許在我把你的臉砸過這窗戶后…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe if I stick your fucking face through this window...{\r}

528
00:31:39,010 --> 00:31:40,550
你就會清楚點
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}you'll get unconfused.{\r}

529
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,420
-把錢他媽的給我 -對不起
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-Give me the fucking money. -I'm sorry.{\r}

530
00:31:42,600 --> 00:31:43,920
我不是故意的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't mean anything by it.{\r}

531
00:31:44,010 --> 00:31:46,640
所以你連錢都準備好了 你他媽的以為我要下注
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's why you had it ready. You thought I was laying it.{\r}

532
00:31:46,810 --> 00:31:49,350
-我的頭 -放聰明點
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-My fucking head. -Smarten up.{\r}

533
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:54,060
而現在尼可拉斯山多羅 要來跟我們說第一總統的故事了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And now Nicholas Santoro will come up and tell us about our first President.{\r}

534
00:31:58,490 --> 00:32:00,990
喬治華盛頓出生在…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}George Washington was born--{\r}

535
00:32:00,990 --> 00:32:03,700
但最起碼還風平浪靜了一陣子
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: But still, it was nice and quiet for a while.{\r}

536
00:32:03,830 --> 00:32:06,400
我們帶著尼奇與珍妮佛滿街亮相…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We presented Nicky and Jennifer all over town...{\r}

537
00:32:06,540 --> 00:32:08,410
像是明星似的
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}like regular Ozzie and Harriets.{\r}

538
00:32:09,710 --> 00:32:11,170
你棒揮得很好
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}COACH: You got a beautiful swing.{\r}

539
00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:14,670
艾斯讓我兒子，小尼奇 參加市區青少棒，真的很好
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Ace got Little Nicky involved with Little League. It was great.{\r}

540
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:18,260
