541
00:32:18,350 --> 00:32:20,880
不過無所謂，這純粹是孩子的事
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}But it didn't matter. It was all about the kids.{\r}

542
00:32:21,020 --> 00:32:23,470
他得明白不是每棒都能揮出全壘打
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He's gotta realize everything can't be a home run.{\r}

543
00:32:23,560 --> 00:32:27,430
我也是這樣告訴他 不過那小子就是這樣
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}That's exactly what I tell him, but that's the kind of kid he is.{\r}

544
00:32:29,190 --> 00:32:32,560
尼奇就是尼奇 他總是引人注目
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: And Nicky being Nicky, he made his presence known.{\r}

545
00:32:32,700 --> 00:32:36,150
尤其是在他不工作的賭場
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Especially at the casino where he definitely did not work...{\r}

546
00:32:36,330 --> 00:32:37,700
大家都明白
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}people got the message.{\r}

547
00:32:37,870 --> 00:32:40,570
就是我，這也是老大為何派我來
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Me, that's why the bosses sent me out here.{\r}

548
00:32:40,710 --> 00:32:43,370
我是來確定 沒有其他人在拿這兒的錢
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I was to make sure no other crews robbed the joint.{\r}

549
00:32:43,500 --> 00:32:45,870
像在那邊的那兩個蠢才
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Like these two fucking balloon heads over here.{\r}

550
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:48,840
想從我們這兒騙走二十萬
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They were gonna try to bang us out of $200, 000.{\r}

551
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:50,630
走著瞧
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, right, I'm sure.{\r}

552
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:52,590
你好嗎？你怎么會在這兒？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}How are you? What are you doing here?{\r}

553
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:53,920
我到這兒來了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I'm over here now.{\r}

