{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}-You're over here? -Yeah, I'm over here with them.{\r}

555
00:33:01,270 --> 00:33:02,730
我們在等卡爾曼
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We're waiting on Carmine.{\r}

556
00:33:02,900 --> 00:33:04,770
是啊，在等卡爾曼
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, we're looking for Carmine.{\r}

557
00:33:04,900 --> 00:33:08,020
他本來在這兒 拿了口箱子后來就走了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}He was here before. He had a suitcase, and then he left.{\r}

558
00:33:08,450 --> 00:33:10,480
