因為基本尊重 我只給別幫家伙一點警告
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Out of respect, guys from other crews got away with a warning.{\r}

569
00:33:44,450 --> 00:33:46,520
其他的人可得小心了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody else, watch out.{\r}

570
00:33:47,780 --> 00:33:49,160
像這群鄉巴佬…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Like these yokels here...{\r}

571
00:33:49,280 --> 00:33:51,790
從沒聽過尼奇或他老家的老大們
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}who never heard of Nicky or the bosses back home.{\r}

572
00:33:51,790 --> 00:33:54,240
這種王八蛋最麻煩了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They're the morons who give you the most trouble.{\r}

573
00:33:54,420 --> 00:33:56,490
被我們抓到后又會溜回來…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}We'd catch them and they'd try to sneak back...{\r}

574
00:33:56,630 --> 00:33:59,160
戴著假胡子、假發、假鼻子
