02:48:38,650 --> 02:48:40,030
多明尼
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}NICKY: Dominick.{\r}

2775
02:49:03,840 --> 02:49:05,090
來吧
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}FRANK: Come on.{\r}

2776
02:49:08,520 --> 02:49:09,970
-埋了他們？ -埋
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}THUG: Bury them? FRANK: Bury them.{\r}

2777
02:49:13,600 --> 02:49:14,640
話放出去了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: The word was out.{\r}

2778
02:49:14,730 --> 02:49:17,350
老大們受夠了尼奇 受夠了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}The bosses had enough of Nicky. They had enough.{\r}

2779
02:49:17,650 --> 02:49:22,230
他們還能忍受多久呢？ 所以拿他們兄弟倆殺雞儆猴
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}How much were they gonna take? So they made an example of him and his brother.{\r}

2780
02:49:23,360 --> 02:49:25,740
他們倆被活埋
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}They buried them while they were still breathing.{\r}

2781
02:49:43,380 --> 02:49:45,420
你還好嗎？小心！
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MAN: You all right? Watch out!{\r}

2782
02:49:51,060 --> 02:49:53,300
-先生，你沒事吧？ -沒事
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MAN: Mister, you all right? SAM: Yeah.{\r}

2783
02:49:55,100 --> 02:49:56,760
他們有別的事給我做
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: They had other ideas for me.{\r}

2784
02:50:06,820 --> 02:50:08,700
我們這兒需要幫忙！
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MEDIC: We need some help over here!{\r}

2785
02:50:10,700 --> 02:50:11,900
你真是幸運
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}MEDIC 2: You sure are lucky, mister.{\r}

2786
02:50:30,640 --> 02:50:32,630
這城市再也不一樣了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: The town will never be the same.{\r}

2787
02:50:33,350 --> 02:50:37,100
在坦吉樂之后，大集團全權掌管
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}After the Tangiers, the big corporations took it all over.{\r}

2788
02:50:38,020 --> 02:50:39,650
今日的賭城像是迪斯奈樂園
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Today it looks like Disneyland.{\r}

2789
02:50:47,870 --> 02:50:49,910
孩子們玩著海盜游戲時…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}While the kids play cardboard pirates...{\r}

2790
02:50:50,040 --> 02:50:53,400
爸爸與媽媽將房貸與大學學費…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Mommy and Daddy drop the house payments and junior's college money...{\r}

2791
02:50:53,540 --> 02:50:55,280
浪費在吃角子老虎機
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}on the poker slots.{\r}

2792
02:50:59,630 --> 02:51:03,160
想當年，莊家知道你的名字 喝什么酒，玩什么牌
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}In the old days, dealers knew your name, what you drank, what you played.{\r}

2793
02:51:03,260 --> 02:51:05,300
今天就像是在機場登記一般
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Today, it's like checking into an airport.{\r}

2794
02:51:05,470 --> 02:51:08,670
你要是叫客房送餐 星期四給你送到就了不起了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}If you order room service, you're lucky if you get it by Thursday.{\r}

2795
02:51:10,010 --> 02:51:13,380
都沒了，一個人拎著 裝著四百萬的皮箱…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Today it's all gone. A whale shows up with $4 million in a suitcase...{\r}

2796
02:51:13,480 --> 02:51:17,850
就有個25歲的旅游系大學畢業生 想要他的身份字號
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and some 25-year-old hotel school kid will want his Social Security number.{\r}

2797
02:51:19,940 --> 02:51:22,100
全美卡車司機工會離開后…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}After the Teamsters got knocked out of the box...{\r}

2798
02:51:22,190 --> 02:51:25,610
大集團幾乎將所有的舊賭場都拆了
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}the corporations tore down practically every one of the old casinos.{\r}

2799
02:51:26,530 --> 02:51:29,400
而蓋新金字塔的錢是從哪來的呢？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And where did the money come from to rebuild the pyramids?{\r}

2800
02:51:30,450 --> 02:51:31,950
垃圾債券
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}Junk bonds.{\r}

2801
02:51:33,410 --> 02:51:35,990
圣地牙哥

2802
02:51:37,420 --> 02:51:38,960
還不確定？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Still not sure?{\r}

2803
02:51:39,630 --> 02:51:41,500
有可能，有些質疑
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: Probable. Maybe questionable.{\r}

2804
02:51:41,590 --> 02:51:44,080
好吧，知道后立即通知我
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: All right, let me know as soon as you can find out.{\r}

2805
02:51:45,470 --> 02:51:48,590
最后，我又回到了起點
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}SAM: In the end, I wound up right back where I started.{\r}

2806
02:51:48,680 --> 02:51:50,470
我還是會選贏家…
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}I could still pick winners...{\r}

2807
02:51:50,600 --> 02:51:53,880
也還是可以為老家 各式各樣的人賺錢
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}and I could still make money for all kinds of people back home.{\r}

2808
02:51:54,060 --> 02:51:55,680
何必搞砸好事呢？
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And why mess up a good thing?{\r}

2809
02:51:57,150 --> 02:51:58,770
就是這樣！
{\fn微軟雅黑}{\fs14}And that's that!{\r}


